The paper proposes a new generative adversarial network for pose transfer, which is a task related to computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also focuses on generating person images, which involves graphics (GR) and multimedia (MM) aspects. The proposed network uses attention mechanisms, which is a popular topic in machine learning (LG) and artificial intelligence (AI).
